OL,3,CFrom Christmas trees to walking sticks
OL,4,C- Metro lost property sold for charity
OL,6,FHundreds of items of lost property
OL,7,Ffound on Metro trains, stations and
OL,8,Fbus interchanges are being sold to
OL,9,Fraise money for a local dementia
OL,10,Fcharity.
OL,12,FNexus the operator of the Metro, is
OL,13,Fselling items which have been found
OL,14,Facross its system over the last two
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FThe sale will take place at Tynemouth
OL,18,FMarket, in Tynemouth Metro station,
OL,19,Fthis Sunday, 7 June.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
