OL,3,CFrom Christmas trees to walking sticks
OL,4,C- Metro lost property sold for charity
OL,6,FItems people can get their hands on
OL,7,Finclude tents and windbreakers,
OL,8,FChristmas trees and cuddly toys.
OL,10,FThere is also brand-new clothing with
OL,11,Ftags on, sports items like basketballs
OL,12,Fand badminton rackets to boxing gloves
OL,13,Fand cycling helmets, jewellery,
OL,14,Fumbrellas, walking sticks, sunglasses
OL,15,Fand more.
OL,17,FMoney from the sale will be donated to
OL,18,FNexus' chosen charity of the year.
OL,19,FThis year, that is North East Dementia
OL,20,FCare, which is a charity based in
OL,21,FSunderland.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
