PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781010670
OL,3,CFrom Christmas trees to walking sticks
OL,4,C- Metro lost property sold for charity
OL,6,FThe organisation is hoping to raise
OL,7,F#35,000 for a new minibus.
OL,9,FNexus say all money raised by the lost
OL,10,Fproperty at the sale, and throughout
OL,11,F2026, will go towards helping them
OL,12,Fachieve this goal.
OL,14,FPublic Affairs Manager at Nexus, Lynne
OL,15,FRobinson, said: "We've raised a lot of
OL,16,Fmoney in previous years with our lost
OL,17,Fproperty auctions and sales. We have a
OL,18,Fweird and wonderful mix of items to
OL,19,Fsell, and we usually get lots of
OL,20,Finterest.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
