PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781010670
OL,3,CFrom Christmas trees to walking sticks
OL,4,C- Metro lost property sold for charity
OL,6,F"It's great to think that the
OL,7,Funclaimed lost property can be put to
OL,8,Fsuch good use, and the funds raised
OL,9,Fwill be welcomed by North East
OL,10,FDementia Care."
OL,12,FThe items on sale at Tynemouth Market
OL,13,Fare cash only and any unsold items
OL,14,Fwill be recycled or donated to charity.
OL,16,FLost property is held by Nexus for 28
OL,17,Fdays before being discarded, recycled
OL,18,For sold, depending on the item and its
OL,19,Fcondition.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]
